=====================
Inventory
Algorithms for: XP, HP, ITEMS, HeroName, 

The Inventory will be able to be seen in the General Store, Outside the General Store on the MAP and inside dungeons. 


=====================
Inventory

Inventory will show: HeroName, ITEMS, XP, HP, and Crystal Spheres

@------------------------@
| Inventory
@------------------------@
| HeroName
| [HP#/HP#]  /  [#XP]
| Moldy Bread [#/#]
| Slimy Chicken [#/#]
| Potions of Health [#/#]
| Extra Lives [#/#]
@------------------------@
| [MagicalSpheres#/MagicalSpheres#]
@------------------------@

EXAMPLE::

@------------------------@
| Inventory
@------------------------@
| Darth Vader
| [97HP/100HP]  /  [11XP]
| Moldy Bread [1/5]
| Slimy Chicken [1/2]
| Potions of Health [0/2]
| Extra Lives [0/9]
@------------------------@
| Magical Spheres [0/1]
@------------------------@

